    "body": "If you add a hook in `PROMPT_COMMAND` before starship, the last status code will be overwritten and hidden from starship. Please try changing your hook to `export PROMPT_COMMAND=\"${PROMPT_COMMAND}; history -a; history -n\"` or try using something like `precmd_functions` from bash-preexec instead.",
